file.content: {"openapi":"3.0.3","info":{"title":"CORS Voorbeeld Calc API","description":"Dit is een demonstratie van de vertalings plugin (i18n) van Goa","version":"1.0"},"servers":[{"url":"http://localhost:80","description":"Default server for calc"}],"paths":{"/add/{a}/{b}":{"get":{"tags":["calc"],"summary":"add calc","description":"Tel twee getallen bij elkaar op en retourneerd het resultaat.","operationId":"calc#add","parameters":[{"name":"a","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","example":1,"format":"int64"},"example":1},{"name":"b","in":"path","required":true,"schema":{"type":"integer","example":2,"format":"int64"},"example":2}],"responses":{"200":{"description":"OK response.","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"type":"integer","example":3,"format":"int64"},"example":3}}}}}}},"components":{},"tags":[{"name":"calc","description":"De reken service stelt basis rekenmethodes publiekelijk beschikbaar"}]}
